Preparing for Agent Engagement

Before using agent engagement, ensure the feature is fully configured.

Workforce Engagement is available in Lightning Experience and requires Enterprise, Performance, or Unlimited Editions.

Configure an Enablement Site (myTrailhead) to Work with Agent Engagement
To configure Workforce Engagement's agent engagement feature, set up a compatible enablement site account and publish custom learning modules.

Configure the Omni-Channel Widget to Work with Agent Engagement
Set up the Omni-Channel widget where Workforce Engagement agents receive learning assignments.

Create and Assign a Learning Manager User Profile for Agent Engagement
Create a Learning Manager user profile to manage agent engagement.

Configure Users as Agent Engagement Learners
Set up users as learners within the agent engagement feature.

Configure Skills for Agent Engagement
Set up skills to work with agent engagement.

title: Preparing for Agent Engagement in Service Cloud
